---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Projects | Everest World Lifts
description: Explore verified elevator, escalator, installation, replacement, and maintenance projects delivered by Everest World Lifts across Nigeria.
navKey: projects
---

<section class="projects-hero">
  <div class="container projects-hero-grid">
    <div class="projects-hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our track record</p>
      <h1>Projects That Keep Nigeria Moving</h1>
      <p>From government complexes to hotels, offices, and homes, our work is built around safe installation, dependable maintenance, and long-term performance.</p>
      <div class="button-group">
        <a href="#project-portfolio" class="btn btn-primary">Explore projects</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss your project</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-hero-media" aria-label="Selected Everest World Lifts project locations">
      <figure class="projects-hero-main">
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/national-assembly.webp" alt="National Assembly Complex in Abuja">
        <figcaption>National Assembly, Abuja</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/rmrdc.webp" alt="Raw Materials Research and Development Council building in Abuja">
        <figcaption>RMRDC, Abuja</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/victoria-island.webp" alt="Aerial view of Victoria Island in Lagos">
        <figcaption>Victoria Island, Lagos</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-overview" aria-label="Project portfolio overview">
  <div class="container project-overview-grid">
    <div><strong>15</strong><span>Verified project records</span></div>
    <div><strong>2008-2016</strong><span>Profile-recorded delivery period</span></div>
    <div><strong>4</strong><span>Core service categories</span></div>
    <div><strong>3</strong><span>Cities represented</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-padding project-portfolio" id="project-portfolio" aria-labelledby="project-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="project-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Delivered experience</p>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="project-title">Every Project, One Standard: Safety First</h2>
      </div>
      <p>These records are drawn from the Everest World Lifts corporate profile. Contract values and private award documents are intentionally not published.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="product-filters project-filters" aria-label="Filter projects by service">
      <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-filter="all" aria-pressed="true">All projects</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-filter="installation" aria-pressed="false">Supply & installation</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-filter="maintenance" aria-pressed="false">Maintenance</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-filter="modernization" aria-pressed="false">Modernization</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-filter="escalators" aria-pressed="false">Escalators</button>
    </div>

    <div class="project-image-note">
      <strong>About the photographs</strong>
      <p>Exact project locations are shown where a reliable public image was available. Cards labelled as a location view use a photograph of the surrounding city or area and do not claim to show the exact building.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-gallery">
      {% for project in projects %}
        <article class="project-card" data-category="{{ project.filter }}">
          <figure class="project-card-image">
            <img src="{{ project.image }}" alt="{{ project.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy">
            <div class="project-card-badges">
              <span>{{ project.year }}</span>
              <span>{{ project.category }}</span>
            </div>
            <figcaption>{{ project.imageContext }}</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <div class="project-card-body">
            <p class="project-service">{{ project.service }}</p>
            <h2>{{ project.client }}</h2>
            <p class="project-location">{{ project.location }}</p>
            <p>{{ project.scope }}</p>
            <a class="project-source" href="{{ project.imageSourceUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image source: {{ project.imageSource }}</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="project-reference">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Need supporting information?</p>
        <h2>Request Project References</h2>
        <p>Talk with our team about relevant experience for your building, equipment, and service requirements.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-dark">Contact our team</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% include "components/cta.njk" %}
